ниторинг с незамедлительным принятием мер.</p><p>С учетом времени на приемку работ, праздничных дней оставляем на контроле до 14.01.2033.</p><p>Приложение: Акт УК, фото, скрин ФКР.</p>","author_name":"Администрация Центрального района","performer":null,"response_performers":[{"id":3381,"name":"ОБЩЕСТВО С ОГРАНИЧЕННОЙ ОТВЕТСТВЕННОСТЬЮ \"ЖИЛКОМСЕРВИС № 1 ЦЕНТРАЛЬНОГО РАЙОНА\" (ИНН 7841384710)"}],"files":[],"photos":[{"id":18761120,"url":"/storage/2/fc1a30ce-99a1-4a13-a436-ab7ac17ecf06.png","original_name":"1.png","thumbnail":"/media/cache/48/90/48900c68ff3faa2be80de78054f4d2d1.png","size":"1600x900"},{"id":18761121,"url":"/storage/2/acba2cfe-465f-429a-95e0-942547ab4b43.jpg","original_name":"2.jpg","thumbnail":"/media/cache/d7/61/d7616af9bc8b510c41b8d9241881fb11.jpg","size":"2480x3507"},{"id":18761122,"url":"/storage/2/5bda383b-f202-4342-ab36-3666073d08a3.jpeg","original_name":"3.jpeg","thumbnail":"/media/cache/b3/d5/b3d5cc7eb6e2eabc82a0a7ea9c0e9c94.jpg","size":"1280x720"},{"id":18761123,"url":"/storage/2/b389d572-0cdd-42f1-8d55-522ef9f6feea.jpeg","original_name":"4.jpeg","thumbnail":"/media/cache/35/08/3508df385e2da88fd7170ba7977a1ef6.jpg","size":"651x1156"},{"id":18761124,"url":"/storage/2/0e99bf01-5905-4aeb-a217-bb86db19abd9.jpeg","original_name":"5.jpeg","thumbnail":"/media/cache/44/17/4417a4e2b54c7c3680a910d78369d6ba.jpg","size":"651x1156"}],"reject":null,"interim_date":"2033-01-14"},"meta":{"title":"Ответ","icon_text":"ПО","icon_title":"Промежуточный ответ","bg_color":"#E3F2FD","border_color":"#536DFE","status_font_color":"#FFFFFF","status_bg_color":"#A5D6A7","icon_bg_color":"#536DFE"},"content_type":28},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13633543","payload":{"id":13633543,"dt":"2021-04-09T11:47:25.529817","status_name":"Рассмотрение","status":3},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-clock-o","icon_bg_color":"#FCAA62"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13625891","payload":{"id":1362